34:06.632 --> 34:10.901
dissolved carbon dioxide
from the atmosphere and

34:11.003 --> 34:15.072
this makes it acidic enough
to dissolve rocks.

34:16.342 --> 34:21.912
Ultimately this water, silt
and locked-up carbon dioxide

34:22.014 --> 34:25.916
will all get washed into
the planet's rivers.

34:28.654 --> 34:33.156
This process goes on right
under our noses every day but

34:33.259 --> 34:37.694
